---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Help Center — Wulong Apps LLC">
  <!-- Help Center Header -->
  <section class="help-hero">
    <div class="help-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container help-hero-content">
      <span class="help-tag animate-in">Support</span>
      <h1 class="animate-in animate-in-delay-1">Help Center</h1>
      <p class="help-hero-subtitle animate-in animate-in-delay-2">Find answers to common questions about your subscription, billing, and account.</p>

      <p class="help-hero-contact animate-in animate-in-delay-3">Can't find what you need? <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Nav -->
  <section class="quick-nav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="quick-nav-grid">
        <a href="#cancel" class="quick-nav-item">
          <div class="quick-nav-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m15 9-6 6"/><path d="m9 9 6 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Cancel Subscription</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#auto-renew" class="quick-nav-item">
          <div class="quick-nav-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 0-9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"/><path d="M3 3v5h5"/><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 0 9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0 6.74-2.74L21 16"/><path d="M16 16h5v5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Auto-Renewal</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#refund" class="quick-nav-item">
          <div class="quick-nav-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Refunds</span>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com" class="quick-nav-item quick-nav-contact">
          <div class="quick-nav-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Email Support</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Don't Recognize a Charge -->
  <section class="section charge-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="charge-card">
        <div class="charge-card-accent"></div>
        <div class="charge-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">Billing</span>
          <h2>Don't Recognize a Charge?</h2>
          <p>Charges from our products appear on your bank or credit card statement as <strong>WULONG LLC</strong> or <strong>STRIPE* WULONG</strong>.</p>
          <p>We operate the following subscription services:</p>
          <div class="charge-products">
            <div class="charge-product">
              <strong>Tinnitus Relief Program</strong>
              <span>tinnitusrelief.io</span>
            </div>
            <div class="charge-product">
              <strong>Remote Jobs Board</strong>
              <span>remotejobsboard.io</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>If you or someone with access to your payment method signed up for one of these services, that explains the charge.</p>
          <p>If you believe the charge is unauthorized, email us at <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a> &mdash; we'll investigate and resolve it within 24 hours.</p>
          <div class="charge-nudge">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
            <span>Please reach out to us before contacting your bank &mdash; we can resolve issues much faster.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-list">
      <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <details id="cancel">
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">How do I cancel my subscription?</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>If you are receiving charges from Wulong Apps LLC, you most likely subscribed directly through one of our product websites and have a web subscription.</p>
            <p>Here are the main characteristics of a Wulong Apps LLC web subscription:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>You paid with a credit/debit card</li>
              <li>You subscribed through our product website (tinnitusrelief.io or remotejobsboard.io)</li>
              <li>The descriptor on your bank statement says "Wulong Apps LLC", "Stripe* Wulong", or a variation</li>
              <li>You received a receipt or welcome email from us (not from Apple or Google)</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>How to Cancel</h4>
            <p><strong>Option 1: Via product website</strong></p>
            <ol>
              <li>Log in to your account on the product website (tinnitusrelief.io or remotejobsboard.io)</li>
              <li>Go to Account Settings</li>
              <li>Find Subscription Details and tap "Cancel Subscription"</li>
            </ol>
            <p><strong>Option 2: Via email</strong></p>
            <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a> with the subject line "Cancel Subscription" and include:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Your full name</li>
              <li>Last 4 digits of your card</li>
              <li>Card brand (Visa, Mastercard, etc.)</li>
              <li>Date of any transaction</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We will process your cancellation within 24 hours.</p>
            <p class="faq-highlight">Once you cancel, your subscription will remain active until the end of the paid period, but you won't be charged again.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details id="auto-renew">
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">Does my subscription automatically renew?</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Yes. All Wulong Apps LLC subscriptions renew automatically until cancelled.</p>
            <h4>Key Points:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Automatic Renewal:</strong> Your plan (weekly, monthly, or 3-month, depending on what you selected) renews at the end of each billing cycle.</li>
              <li><strong>Trial Periods:</strong> If your subscription begins with a discounted introductory offer, it will automatically convert to the full subscription rate you selected unless cancelled before the introductory period ends.</li>
              <li><strong>Billing:</strong> At each renewal, your selected payment method will be charged automatically to ensure uninterrupted access.</li>
              <li><strong>Cancellation:</strong> To avoid renewal charges, you must cancel before the renewal date. Closing the browser or deleting bookmarks does not cancel your subscription.</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>How to Cancel:</h4>
            <p><strong>Website Purchases:</strong> Cancel directly on the product website under Account Settings, or by emailing <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">I didn't authorize a subscription or recurring charge</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>When you subscribed, you were clearly presented with:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Any applicable introductory price (if offered)</li>
              <li>The subscription rate that applies after the introductory period (weekly, monthly, or 3-month, depending on your choice)</li>
              <li>The fact that the subscription renews automatically unless cancelled</li>
            </ul>
            <p>By confirming your purchase, you provided explicit authorization for Wulong Apps LLC (and our payment processor, Stripe) to charge your selected payment method on a recurring basis until you cancel.</p>
            <h4>Key Points:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Automatic Renewal:</strong> Subscriptions renew automatically at the end of each billing cycle.</li>
              <li><strong>Cancellation Deadline:</strong> You must cancel before your renewal date to avoid further charges.</li>
              <li><strong>Active Cancellation Required:</strong> Closing the browser or deleting bookmarks does not cancel your subscription. To stop charges, you must cancel via your account settings or email us.</li>
              <li><strong>Billing Authorization:</strong> By subscribing, you authorized Wulong Apps LLC to charge your payment method for recurring fees until you cancel.</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>How to Cancel:</h4>
            <p>Log in to the product website &rarr; Account Settings &rarr; Subscription Details &rarr; Cancel Subscription.</p>
            <p>Or email us at <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a>. Send your full name, last 4 digits of the card, card brand (Visa, Mastercard, etc.), and date of any transaction so we can locate your subscription.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">I was unaware of the charges</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Our products are premium subscription-based services. To create an account and access premium features, it is necessary to select a subscription plan and provide a valid payment method.</p>
            <h4>Key Points:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Subscription Choice Required:</strong> You cannot complete sign-up without selecting a subscription plan and explicitly confirming your purchase.</li>
              <li><strong>Transparent Pricing:</strong> The subscription price, billing period, and any applicable introductory offer are displayed on-screen before you complete your purchase.</li>
              <li><strong>Automatic Renewal:</strong> Subscriptions renew automatically at the end of each billing cycle unless cancelled in advance.</li>
              <li><strong>Billing Authorization:</strong> By confirming your purchase, you authorized Wulong Apps LLC (and its payment processor, Stripe) to charge your selected payment method on a recurring basis until you cancel.</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>Important Notes:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Closing the browser or deleting bookmarks does not cancel your subscription.</li>
              <li>To prevent future charges, you must actively cancel your subscription through your account settings or by emailing us.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Need help? Email <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a> and we'll assist you right away.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details id="refund">
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">How do I get a refund?</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com">contact@wulongllc.com</a> with your account email and the reason for your refund request.</p>
            <p>We review all refund requests and typically respond within 24 hours. We're happy to work with you to find a resolution.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            <span class="summary-text">What payment methods do you accept?</span>
            <span class="summary-icon"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>We process all payments securely through <strong>Stripe</strong>, which accepts all major credit and debit cards including Visa, Mastercard, American Express, and Discover.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Need More Help -->
  <section class="section callout-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="help-callout">
        <div class="callout-inner">
          <div class="callout-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Need More Help?</h3>
          <p>We're here for any billing or account question you may have.</p>
          <a href="mailto:contact@wulongllc.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Email Us at contact@wulongllc.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  // Auto-open FAQ details when navigating via hash (quick nav or footer links)
  function openTargetFaq() {
    const hash = window.location.hash?.slice(1);
    if (!hash) return;
    const target = document.getElementById(hash);
    if (target && target.tagName === 'DETAILS') {
      target.open = true;
      target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    }
  }
  openTargetFaq();
  window.addEventListener('hashchange', openTargetFaq);
</script>

<style>
  /* Help Hero */
  .help-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .help-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 30% 20%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 70% 80%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-bg-warm) 0%, var(--color-bg) 100%);
  }

  .help-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .help-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .help-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .help-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .help-hero-contact {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  }

  .help-hero-contact a {
    color: var(--color-amber);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Quick Nav */
  .quick-nav {
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: -40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .quick-nav-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quick-nav-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 28px 16px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line-subtle);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quick-nav-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .quick-nav-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .quick-nav-item:hover .quick-nav-icon {
    background: var(--color-amber-light);
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .quick-nav-contact .quick-nav-icon {
    background: var(--color-amber-light);
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  /* Charge Section */
  .charge-section {
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .charge-card {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line-subtle);
    display: flex;
  }

  .charge-card-accent {
    width: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-amber) 0%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.2) 100%);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .charge-card-body {
    padding: 44px 44px 44px 40px;
  }

  .charge-card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .charge-card p {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .charge-products {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .charge-product {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .charge-product strong {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .charge-product span {
    color: var(--color-ink-faint);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .charge-nudge {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--color-amber-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--color-amber-hover);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .charge-nudge svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  details {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  details:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-line);
  }

  details[open] {
    border-color: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.15);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  summary {
    padding: 22px 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  summary:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .summary-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .summary-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .summary-icon::before,
  .summary-icon::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    background: var(--color-ink-soft);
    border-radius: 1px;
    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .summary-icon::before {
    width: 12px;
    height: 1.5px;
  }

  .summary-icon::after {
    width: 1.5px;
    height: 12px;
  }

  details[open] .summary-icon {
    background: var(--color-amber-light);
  }

  details[open] .summary-icon::before {
    background: var(--color-amber);
  }

  details[open] .summary-icon::after {
    background: var(--color-amber);
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-content {
    padding: 0 28px 28px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .faq-content p {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .faq-content h4 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .faq-content ul,
  .faq-content ol {
    margin: 10px 0 18px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .faq-content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 4px;
  }

  .faq-content li::marker {
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .faq-content a {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .faq-highlight {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-amber);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  /* Callout */
  .callout-section {
    padding-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .help-callout {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--color-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .help-callout::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .callout-inner {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 64px 48px;
  }

  .callout-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .help-callout h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .help-callout p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .help-hero {
      padding: 64px 0 80px;
    }

    .quick-nav {
      margin-top: -32px;
    }

    .quick-nav-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .charge-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .charge-card-accent {
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
    }

    .charge-card-body {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .charge-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .charge-products {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    summary {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .faq-content {
      padding: 0 20px 20px;
    }

    .callout-inner {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .help-callout h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .quick-nav-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .quick-nav-item {
      padding: 20px 12px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }
  }
</style>
